name: Resume Templates - Free to Use!
description:
Free resume templates for you to apply for jobs. We made this for you so you don't need to spend your time designing a Resume, because you should focus on what's more important––finding a job. We wish you all the best on the job hunt.

You can also download the Microsoft Word / Google Docs / PDF version at: https://gum.co/ONhCDq (insert zero when asked to pay).

We hope these templates are helpful to you. Send us your feedback to betterexperience.design@gmail.com
